featured_reviews.review_id:
Magnificently built in Indo-Persian style with beautiful skyscraper minarets and dome (Qubba).  Ample parking space.

Excellent amenities.  Spacious 'Vuzookhana'   (place for making ablution for prayers) in accordance with the rulings of the Hanafi school of Fiq'h.

Separate facility for ladies provided. Convenient congregational prayer (jama'ath) timings.

Jumu'a Khutba (Friday sermon) in Arabic Language starts at 1 pm. Admonition speech  in local language before the formal Friday sermon.

Though the Masjid is located in the heart of the busy town, we may not feel it inside.

Really spiritual atmosphere which soothes aching hearts.

featured_reviews.review_id:
A conveniently  located  Jumu'ah masjid with all essential amenities.  Ladies prayer space available in the masjid. Essential  parking facility.

Walkable distance from the town centre and the Town Juma Masjid.

Managed by Kerala  Nadvathul Mujahideen, the major Salafi faction in Kerala.

The formal Friday sermon (Jumu'ah Khutba) is delivered in Malayalam.

First Salafi Masjid in the district.
